  <h1>üìå MyHotPicks ‚Äì Global Independent Voting by Fans</h1>
  <p><strong>MyHotPicks</strong> is an independent and global fan platform created to give voice to the audience ‚Äî the fans ‚Äî in the world of beauty pageants.</p>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>üí¨ Our Mission</h2>
    <p>To celebrate, highlight and value the work of candidates, organizations, and sponsors, through free and democratic fan participation.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>üéØ How it works</h2>
    <p>Each registered user of the platform selects <strong>10 candidates</strong> from any competition and ranks them in order of preference.</p>
    <p>Each position awards a specific number of points:</p>

    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Position</th><th>Points Given</th></tr>
